{
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "ref": "sign-of-cross"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": {
        "en-US": "Divine Mercy Novena",
        "pt-BR": "Novena da Divina Miseric\u00f3rdia"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rubric",
      "text": {
        "en-US": "Offer today's intention and prayer, then pray the Divine Mercy Chaplet.",
        "pt-BR": "Ofere\u00e7a a inten\u00e7\u00e3o e a ora\u00e7\u00e3o do dia e, em seguida, reze o Ter\u00e7o da Miseric\u00f3rdia."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "cycle",
      "data": "novena-days",
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "subheading",
          "text": "{{dayTitle}}"
        },
        {
          "type": "meditation",
          "text": "{{meditation}}"
        },
        {
          "type": "divider"
        },
        {
          "type": "rubric",
          "text": {
            "en-US": "Today's intention:",
            "pt-BR": "Inten\u00e7\u00e3o do dia:"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "rubric",
          "text": "{{intention}}"
        },
        {
          "type": "divider"
        },
        {
          "type": "rubric",
          "text": {
            "en-US": "Prayer for this intention:",
            "pt-BR": "Ora\u00e7\u00e3o por esta inten\u00e7\u00e3o:"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "prayer",
          "inline": "{{petitionText}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "text": {
        "en-US": "Divine Mercy Chaplet",
        "pt-BR": "Ter\u00e7o da Miseric\u00f3rdia Divina"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "ref": "our-father"
    },
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "ref": "hail-mary"
    },
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "ref": "apostles-creed"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "repeat",
      "count": 5,
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "rubric",
          "text": {
            "en-US": "On the Our Father bead:",
            "pt-BR": "Na conta do Pai Nosso:"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "prayer",
          "ref": "eternal-father"
        },
        {
          "type": "rubric",
          "text": {
            "en-US": "On each of the ten Hail Mary beads:",
            "pt-BR": "Em cada uma das dez contas da Ave Maria:"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "repeat",
          "count": 10,
          "sections": [
            {
              "type": "prayer",
              "ref": "divine-mercy-response"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "divider"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "rubric",
      "text": {
        "en-US": "Concluding prayer (three times):",
        "pt-BR": "Ora\u00e7\u00e3o final (tr\u00eas vezes):"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "repeat",
      "count": 3,
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "prayer",
          "ref": "holy-god"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "inline": {
        "en-US": "Eternal God, in whom mercy is endless and the treasury of compassion inexhaustible, look kindly upon us and increase Your mercy in us, that in difficult moments we might not despair nor become despondent, but with great confidence submit ourselves to Your holy will, which is Love and Mercy itself.\nAmen.",
        "pt-BR": "Deus Eterno, em quem a miseric\u00f3rdia \u00e9 infinita e o tesouro de compaix\u00e3o inesgot\u00e1vel, olhai bondosamente para n\u00f3s e aumentai em n\u00f3s a Vossa miseric\u00f3rdia, para que em momentos dif\u00edceis n\u00e3o nos desesperemos nem desanimemos, mas com grande confian\u00e7a nos submetamos \u00e0 Vossa santa vontade, que \u00e9 o pr\u00f3prio Amor e Miseric\u00f3rdia.\nAm\u00e9m."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "prayer",
      "ref": "sign-of-cross"
    }
  ]
}
